{"tid":2450631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗斥美國向金融機構施壓可恥","createTime":"2021-03-17T14:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T15:21:25.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfa23e0646b38523869a99cce950740934d4211","tid":2450631,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"頭條<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗斥美國向金融機構施壓 將續為國家及香港貢獻<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院制裁24名中國和香港官員，指削弱香港自治，包括早前被列入制裁名單的全國人大常委譚耀宗，譚耀宗批評美方行為可恥。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗表示，美方向金融機構施壓的行為可恥，又引述全國人大常委會副委員長王晨，指他在全國人大會議上，已經強烈批評有關的脅迫行為。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗又指，任何國家都無權以任何藉口，干涉香港的內部事務，重申香港特區事務完全屬於中國內政，表明會一如既往，努力參與全國人大常委會的工作，繼續真誠為國家及香港作應有貢獻。"},{"pid":"8eb1ba1558675657eef0e26fc7992ba667a1c4eb","tid":2450631,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"王冬勝?"},{"pid":"3eac6f2f60dea2e219c7ba0b1ece73fcf199da6a","tid":2450631,"uid":104425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"估唔到泛民成日講嘅嘢，會變成痰尿盅講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗唔洗講埋今日係香港金融界最黑暗嘅一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8b8990907a37cf09f0c160414863705734e274","tid":2450631,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"支那仲要理美帝制裁，就唔夠威啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗仲唔反制？"},{"pid":"a9d0b2e039b12660d71d68503c7b17c9afdebf59","tid":2450631,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"驚啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cbdec4425f1ca28f0c1227445e8bd8f64c0935","tid":2450631,"uid":53922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"屌你有東莞銀行，驚閪咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98c4d086c89a5b7